<paragraph blockId="95.[192,1440,291,379]" pageId="95" pageNumber="94">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[192,324,291,315]" pageId="95" pageNumber="94">Remarks.</emphasis>
Not easily distinguished from other non maculate species, 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Gordon and Hanley" authorityYear="2017" box="[1045,1147,291,315]" class="Insecta" family="Coccinellidae" genus="Prodilis" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="95" pageNumber="94" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="lynda">
